data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home nestled in the desirable Hidden Meadow subdivision. Spacious open concept 1-story fully remodeled with a 2-year-old roof.  The backyard is perfect for outdoor entertaining and includes a 2-year-old above-ground pool, or if removed, a leveled sand area perfect for a fire pit.  Conveniently located near I-10, Beltway 8 & Highway 90. Zoned to Sheldon ISD and a short drive to W. Lake Houston shopping areas.  Perfect for a permanent residence or investment property!
